title: TomatoDialogue0
---
Tomato: Oh, hey there! I'm just a humble tomato, but I have some juicy secrets to share. Did you know that tomatoes are actually fruits? Yeah, it's true! We may be used in savory dishes, but botanically speaking, we're classified as fruits because we develop from the ovary of a flower and contain seeds. So next time you see me in a salad or on a pizza, remember that I'm not just a vegetable, I'm a delicious fruit with a lot of flavor!
===
